<tree text="Yamakappakara&#x1E47;a-a&#x1E6D;&#x1E6D;hakath&#x101;" target="text">
  <text>
    <gatha type="1">Saṅkhepeneva  devānaṃ, devadevo surālaye;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Kathāvatthuppakaraṇaṃ, desayitvā raṇañjaho.</gatha>
    <gatha type="1">Yamassa visayātīto, nānāyamakamaṇḍitaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Abhidhammappakaraṇaṃ, chaṭṭhaṃ chaṭṭhāna desako.</gatha>
    <gatha type="1">Yamakaṃ ayamāvatta-nīlāmalatanūruho;</gatha>
    <gatha type="2">Yaṃ desayi anuppatto, tassa saṃvaṇṇanākkamo;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Idāni yasmā tasmāssa, hoti saṃvaṇṇanā ayanti.</gatha>
  </text>
</tree>
